Rating: 4
ALERT! 75 minutes is entirely too long! I roasted mine in a convection oven at 425 degrees -- and 20 minutes is absolutely sufficient! Anything more and the squash will be mush! Having said that, this is a wonderfully simple and delicious recipe. I prepared it for a dinner party over the weekend and everyone served themselves twice! I recommend that you eliminate the potatoes and increase the beets -- in fact, next time I think I'll try to find some orange beets to add to the melange!

