Delicious and nutritious! For 2 people, we used 1/2 red onion, 3 small potatoes halved, 2 beets quartered, 1/2 acorn squash cut in 1" chunks, 5 cloves of garlic. Baked for 1/2 hour.

Rating: 3
There are several excellent roasted root veggie recipes but none can be easier than this (or healthier). Made for thanksgiving this year and several folks requested the recipe. I'll definately do this again... loved the the flavors & the color combo of these veggies (which would be even better with minimal post roasting mixing - ie. if you add enough salt and pepper before baking - be very generous with the salt & pepper ). And no, you really don't need to peel the beets - just scrub well and trim.

